'''Foldsjøen''' is a [[reservoir]] in the municipalities of [[Surnadal]] and [[Rindal]] in [[Møre og Romsdal]] counties, [[Norway]]. The lake is [[dam]]med from the [[Folda (Rindal)|Folda River]] and the water is used in the Trollheim power station. Slightly more elevated and directly to the south is the [[Gråsjøen]] reservoir, which is also behind a hydro-power dam.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yr.no/place/Norway/M%C3%B8re_og_Romsdal/Rindal/Foldsj%C3%B8en/|title=Foldsjøen|publisher=[[yr.no]]|language=Norwegian|accessdate=2010-12-07}}</ref>

