{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}} [[File:IFMSA National Member Organisations - World Map.svg|500px|right]] {{Update|part=the list of IFMSA NMOs|updated=August 2012 (inconsistent future edits since then)|date=September 2018}}
'''List of IFMSA member organisations'''. [[International Federation of Medical Students' Associations|International Federation of Medical Students' Associations (IFMSA)]] as an [[umbrella organization|umbrella organisation]] embraces 135 national and local organisations in 125 [[country|countries]] and/or [[Area_(country_subdivision)|areas]] on 5 [[region]]s. Of these 135 organisations only 106 have full membership status while 12 are candidates for full membership and 7 are associated with IFMSA <small>(2018)</small><ref name="IFMSA.org">{{cite web |title=IFMSA National Member Organizations |url=https://ifmsa.org/national-member-organizations/ |website=IFMSA Members |accessdate=23 September 2018 |language=English}}</ref>.
Some countries such as Spain have two member organisations in [[International Federation of Medical Students' Associations|IFMSA]] since [[Catalonia]] has a locale organisation, AECS, whereas the rest of Spain is organised under IFMSA-Spain. Other counties such as [[Brazil]] have two national organisations that are both members of IFMSA.
All organisations are divided into 5 [[region]]s. There are 22 organisations in Africa, 18 in Asia-Pacific, 17 in the Eastern-Mediterranean Region (EMR), 48 in Europe and 30 in the Americas <small>(2018)</small>.<ref name="IFMSA.org"></ref>
Member organisations in IFMSA <small>(Number of members includes both medical and other students)</small><ref name="IFMSA.net">{{cite web|url=http://ifmsa.net/public/nmolist.php |publisher= International Federation of Medical Students' Associations |title=IFMSA National Member Organisations List|accessdate=17 August 2012}}</ref>:
